Doctor's Note: Coronavirus and 'underlying health conditions'
What are the underlying health conditions that put you more at risk from coronavirus and how can you protect yourself?
People with asthma have a higher risk of complications from COVID-19 [David McNew/Getty Images/AFP]
MORE ON HEALTH
